{"tid":761685,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"韓女團MV仿A片拍攝！預告釋出性暗示強烈 破格演出再度引發爭議","createTime":"2018-07-30T14:55:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-31T17:06:14.000Z","uid":3189,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f14da8dc682c40ebfdfc6fd480389db6b1c33282","tid":761685,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T14:55:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ychz29L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fychz29L.png&h=b2effeac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n曾因一身粉色緊身衣而被網友戲稱「香腸姑娘」的女團Six Bomb，昨天官方SNS發佈了將在7月31日回歸的預告短片，然而破格的內容讓韓網友大喊：也太誇張了吧！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/hLAwjCx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FhLAwjCx.png&h=5d99c368&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n預告短片中的開頭就仿被分級的影片一樣，以警告標示作為起始。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/H4kmJ5F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FH4kmJ5F.png&h=92f6434f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n接著就會看到成員們一個個仿日本成人片一樣，穿著清涼的躺在床上，或是衣著暴露的接受訪問，甚至後製還特別加上日文字來增加相似度。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Lr5D9yz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FLr5D9yz.png&h=491332d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n甚至連用馬賽克遮住男子的臉這種暗示意味超濃厚的畫面都出籠......讓韓國網友大呼這公司真是越來越沒有下限了！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P_lE3istXYw&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DP_lE3istXYw%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=rOai4qxVptJ7VVmcqwObHQHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=842bbb75\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P_lE3istXYw&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n釋出的預告短片在影音平台Youtube上也被設置了年齡分級。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G6sdBeGv2Yc&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DG6sdBeGv2Yc%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=rOai4qxVptJ7VVmcqwObHQHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=146906e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G6sdBeGv2Yc&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n其實Six Bomb會開始被大眾注意是因為在2016年發行的&lt;等10年吧，寶貝&gt;這首歌的MV當中穿著「香腸裝」，惡趣味的服裝甚至導致她們被各大電視台聯合封殺。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/3n8bUn8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F3n8bUn8.jpg&h=3e8c68f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但Six Bomb即使被封殺也不改另類風格，接著在2017年以整型為概念發行&lt;變漂亮Before&gt;及&lt;變漂亮After&gt;兩首歌，MV中拍攝成員到整型診所接受諮詢，以及整形後再出發的樣子。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ITqx4ZbqGpo&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DITqx4ZbqGpo%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=rOai4qxVptJ7VVmcqwObHQHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=d6f1eefa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ITqx4ZbqGpo&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n在韓國整型一直是一個時常被討論的話題，而成員們甚至在採訪中爆料成員4名就花了韓幣1億元（約台幣272萬元）來整形。<br />\n<br />\n想在競爭激烈的韓國娛樂圈搏出頭而出奇招的方式並不讓人感到意外，然而這樣破尺度的風格還是讓韓網友們希望公司能夠為團員著想，不要毀了這些女孩們呀！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.wishnote.tw/contents/?contentsId=97981\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.wishnote.tw%2Fcontents%2F%3FcontentsId%3D97981&d=rOai4qxVptJ7VVmcqwObHQHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=789034ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.wishnote.tw/contents/?contentsId=97981</a>"},{"pid":"98d27519deaab440777be6e83353b306b6bcd2fb","tid":761685,"uid":49664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T15:30:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FsqP8zMD-Yo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFsqP8zMD-Yo&d=rOai4qxVptJ7VVmcqwObHQHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=f14534f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FsqP8zMD-Yo</a>"},{"pid":"c7c7fa9b7cc82e2016f47be58aa1576034facdef","tid":761685,"uid":49664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T15:30:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/31/233044_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f